                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-186-off999 t18180114-186-crimeloc1002"></join>. The prisoner, and another man, came to my house, and called for a pint of beer; I was in the cellar, and heard a noise, I came up, and found the prisoner in the passage, where he had no business - I saw him take the measure from under his coat; he went out, I followed, seized him, and took it from him.</p>
